					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I dunno. I love the idea, but the writing is kinda meh, it's not bringing across the screaming terror inherent in the concept. It doesn't help that we've had a couple of pamphlets that permanently change your way of thinking come up recently, and this just isn't as clever as (say) the magic 6-ball.</p> <p>Also, nitpickingly: Australia has nine different police forces, none of which is actually called the &quot;Australian Police Force&quot;. Pick a state or territory, or just say &quot;local police&quot;.</p> 
